</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#F4D99F FACE=arial>
<P>> I am a Wood Elf from the village of

<BR>&gt; Kelethin. High atop the trees there is
<BR>&gt; plenty of business going around. But one
<BR>&gt; thing I can't find there is the blacksmith.
<BR>&gt; Has anyone found him? I looked on the map
<BR>&gt; and it seems there is no bridge to his
<BR>&gt; platform. If anyone could just give me
<BR>&gt; directions to where he is, I would be most
<BR>&gt; grateful. Please send your response to
<BR>&gt; Ractoon007@hotmail.com
<BR>Are you lookin for the Forge? it is located to the left of the lift closest to the newbie hunting grounds, just go left from that lift and go forward tthru two more and you should see the forge. You just have to explore the city and check all the vendors cause different ones sell
<BR>the items you will need to smith. I did hear you have to go to the steamfront mountains to get
<BR>sharpening stones, but most everything else ya need is in Kelethin or the dwarf city.
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
